text: Francis Blase Delehanty (1859-1932) circa 1915 Francis Blase Delehanty (February 3, 1859 - October 7, 1932) was a justice of the New York Supreme Court. ==Biography== He was born on February 3, 1859 to Michael Delehanty and Mary Quinn in Albany, New York. He married Annie Ceclia. He died on October 7, 1932. ==References== Category:New York Supreme Court Justices Category:1859 births Category:1932 deaths
